{"tid":2089460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"誠懇呼籲唔好去英國住，你唔係英國人又去英國住，英國人會好反感","createTime":"2020-07-01T16:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T13:01:54.000Z","uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3a5efad7af87df6d63685c5b5db39f7514553ddd","tid":2089460,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:23:39.000Z","msg":"誠懇呼籲唔好去英國住，你唔係英國人又去英國住，英國人會好反感"},{"pid":"308969b4ee7a7426a72d3d07e0941211ab010784","tid":2089460,"uid":6103,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:24:21.000Z","msg":"死5毛又開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f735567bdaf87f124731e6fc709051b7818bb1","tid":2089460,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:24:30.000Z","msg":"連登知名5毛：回憶小子"},{"pid":"a982976c23cca82e8a44af057a7ca828cde9b03b","tid":2089460,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:27:31.000Z","msg":"五毛配合港共語調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府其實好驚BNO班人真係走<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2089353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2089353</a>"},{"pid":"62b8e9a420f6a96315767bc810143c311b251bab","tid":2089460,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:32:01.000Z","msg":"借個位，BNO平權正視聽<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑色五毛分化警告，大量五毛正在用藍絲有BNO、走人對唔住97後割97後等風向進行分化</span></span></strong>，大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n1.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家比人拉過/有小朋友（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）的話就應該即刻走</span></span></strong>，其他人亦應該起碼做好隨時走既準備，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">香港抗爭運動已經由本土抗爭升級為準國際戰爭， 我們能做的十分有限。 相反大家離開或準備好隨時可以離開，則美國及其盟友可以隨時採取行動，對香港進行制裁，令香港達至零經濟活動，攬炒香港經濟， 甚至日後作出軍事行動亦無需擔心誤傷香港人。</span></span></strong> 而且大家亦可用移民理由提取所有資產及強積金進一步<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打擊香港的財政儲備</span></span></strong>。<br />\n而且多人走亦可以起到掩護最需要走既手足，救奶左野手足係目前最重要既事。<br />\n<br />\n2.大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無需擔心藍絲以及黑警移民英國</span></span></strong>，藍絲得兩種a.垃圾b.收成期，a.涯唔到六年移民監b.揾錢唔捨得走/走要承受巨大損失<br />\n<br />\n重點：大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不應該反對平權或推到現階段設立篩選，因為這樣會妨礙奶左野手足逃難</span></span></strong>。反而，大家應該在藍絲移民英國後再篤灰。大家，要記住，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">篤灰係一把藍絲頭上既利劍，一日未入籍一日都嚮度，我就係要佢地嚮英國每一日都擔心比人篤灰，呢樣恐懼做為懲罰先係最大懲罰</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">97後手足唔會被割</span></span></strong>，首先，佢地可以跟BNO父母及配偶前往英國。第二，對於<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">未受BNO平權保障嘅人佢哋仲有美國既救生艇計劃</span></span></strong>，該計劃估計幾日內亦會通過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">樓主五毛</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"40a09d971a68ae9fc86e4f979ad465b859e77c20","tid":2089460,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:50:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">連<br />\n登<br />\n日<br />\n報<br />\n｜<br />\n支<br />\n持<br />\n獨<br />\n裁<br />\n政<br />\n權<br />\n者<br />\n，<br />\n無<br />\n權<br />\n享<br />\n有<br />\n言<br />\n論<br />\n自<br />\n由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n請<br />\n問<br />\n回憶小子<br />\n(狗隻#149494)<br />\n你<br />\n屙<br />\n尿<br />\n嗰<br />\n陣<br />\n起<br />\n左<br />\n腳<br />\n定<br />\n右<br />\n腳<br />\n?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1926109\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1926109</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"a02734a1306be588b03df9f4caae71ca06140442","tid":2089460,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T13:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}